name: Dino Jump (Fusion Game)
description:
Help the Dino go through all cities of Earth. Avoid vehicles and enemy Birds! 

Has it ever happened to you when you do not have internet that funny dinosaur appears?

 You are a Dinosaur in a world, jump to avoid vehicles and birds. Unlock new cities . How far can you run and jump in this adventurous game. Run in the endless tracks of beautiful and scary cities with your Dino Make more and more High scores and beat your own score.
